    <item>
      <title>My shortcode for PlantUML</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-plantuml/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-plantuml/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;My shortcode to create diagrams with PlantUML.
This shortcode uses Kroki to render PlantUML diagrams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Example&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;example&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#example&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The following example shows how to use the shortcode and its rendered output.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Code&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;{{&amp;lt; plantuml &amp;gt;}}
class Person {
  -id: long
  &amp;#43;getId():long
  &amp;#43;setId(id: long)
}
{{&amp;lt; /plantuml &amp;gt;}}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copied!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Result&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id=&#34;plantuml-1776738758886672000&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;script&gt;
(async function() {
  const diagram = `\n@startuml\n!theme plain\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam monochrome true\nskinparam classAttributeIconSize 0\nhide stereotype\nhide circle\n\nclass Person \u007b\n  -id: long\n  \u002bgetId():long\n  \u002bsetId(id: long)\n\u007d\n\n@enduml\n`;

  const res = await fetch(&#34;https://kroki.io/plantuml/svg&#34;, {
    method: &#34;POST&#34;,
    headers: { &#34;Content-Type&#34;: &#34;text/plain&#34; },
    body: diagram
  });

  const output = await res.text();
  document.getElementById(&#34;plantuml-1776738758886672000&#34;).innerHTML = output;
})();
&lt;/script&gt;


      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>My shortcode for Questions</title>
