      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-for-questions/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;This shortcode is useful for displaying questions with hidden solutions. Question numbers and answer option letters are automatically generated.
This shortcode supports &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-plantuml&#34;&gt;PlantUML&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/shortcode-code&#34;&gt;code&lt;/a&gt; rendering shortcodes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Usage&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;usage&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#usage&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The following example shows how to use the shortcode and its rendered output.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Code&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

